trans-unit.source: Provides a base implementation of a channel object that exposes a dictionary interface to its properties.
trans-unit.target: 提供要將字典介面公開 (Expose) 至其屬性之通道物件的基底實作。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelObjectWithProperties> is the base class for <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> and <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelObjectWithProperties> 是基底類別<xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties>和<xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> and <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties> can be used as the base classes for channels and channel sinks that provide named properties.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> 和<xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties>可以做為基底類別的通道和通道接收提供具名屬性。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelObjectWithProperties> handles the complex task of asking a channel object for its properties.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelObjectWithProperties> 處理要求通道物件其屬性的複雜工作。

trans-unit.source: This class makes a link demand and an inheritance demand at the class level.
trans-unit.target: 此類別可讓連結要求和繼承要求在類別層級。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Security.SecurityException> is thrown when either the immediate caller or the derived class does not have infrastructure permission.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Security.SecurityException>立即呼叫者或衍生的類別沒有基礎結構的權限時，會擲回。

trans-unit.source: For details about security demands, see [Link Demands](~/docs/framework/misc/link-demands.md) and [Inheritance Demands](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).
trans-unit.target: 如需安全性需求的詳細資訊，請參閱[連結要求](~/docs/framework/misc/link-demands.md)和[繼承要求](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9)。

trans-unit.source: For operating with infrastructure code.
trans-unit.target: 營運與基礎結構程式碼。

trans-unit.source: Demand value: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.InheritanceDemand" />; Permission value: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag.Infrastructure" />
trans-unit.target: 要求的值： <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.InheritanceDemand" />;權限的值： <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag.Infrastructure" />

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the collection of properties in the channel object is read-only.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the dictionary of channel object properties is synchronized.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出通道物件屬性的字典是否已經同步 (Synchronize)。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the dictionary of channel object properties is synchronized; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果通道物件屬性的字典已經同步，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。
